ygData.messageBody:
Duster V and Duster X give no faction hits
I've never cleaned any of the cleaners or scrubbers though, and I'm not
keen to..
Though when I was playing my dwarf and doing the metal rat quest, I killed
the cleaner X that was in Kaladim, and took a faction hit with "Clockwork
gnome", a faction I hadn't seen before.. As well as dropping the scrap
metal required for the dwarf quest, the cleaner also dropped a "Bozanite
pestle", a no -drop lore item that looked like a metal rod, though turning
it in with the scrap did nothing.
